1. Considered approved and taken on record the Unaudited Financial Results (Standalone and Consolidated) (UFRs) of the Company for the quarter and nine months ended on December 31 2024 pursuant to Regulation 33 of SEBI LODR Regulations (enclosed herewith as an Annexure - 1); 
2. Taken on record the Limited Review Report of S. S. Kothari Mehta & Co. LLP Chartered Accountants (Statutory Auditors) on the above UFRs (enclosed herewith as an Annexure - 1); and
3. The Board of Directors on the basis of due recommendations of Nomination & Remuneration Committee (NRC) approved the appointment of Mr. Sanyam Nagpal as Vice President (VP) Business [Senior Management Personnel (SMP)] w.e.f. February 07 2025.
